cuddling with jimin is not always innocent

“baaaaaaabe.” you say, for the ninth time just that hour, you may or may not have smiled at another man.. in which jimin did not like because he, as a genuinely jealous person pretty much got jealous if you even looked at another man for a bit longer than needed.

so ever since the two of you got home he had been giving you the silent treatment which didn’t really settle with you, so while he was ‘doing’ something on his phone looking distracted you tried to get his attention with cringy aegyo and pinching his cheeks. at one point you tried sit behind him on the couch with him between your legs and back hugging him, you knew that was his sweet spot and he loved it when you did that. you were getting tired of it, it was late and you wanted to go to sleep with you cuddling into his side because you couldn’t sleep without him.

“jimin.. don’t ignore me anymore please.”

you said with a huff before standing up and leaving him on the couch to get ready for bed, as you walked to the bathroom you felt his eyes on you but didn’t bother turning around feeling too tired and just wanting to go to sleep. after brushing your teeth you brushed your teeth and took of the remaining makeup you had on your face before turing the lights off and going into the bedroom, where you found jimin laying in his back with his phone still in his hand. he glanced up at you with red cheeks before looking down at his phone again and you wondered what the hell had his cheeks red.

because usually only you would turn his cheeks red like that, you decided to push it away and walk over to your shared wardrobe and finding your usual pyjamas which consisted of underwear and jimin’s oversized white t-shirt that you had stolen many moons ago.

taking off your clothes in front of jimin was no unusual thing, you both did it occasionally so you payed no mind to it and started stripping. after changing into your pyjamas you walked over to your side of the bed and slipped under the covers. jimin was still on his phone but you nudged him and he looked over at you, “are you done being mad? i want to cuddle with you..” you said intertwining you hand with his and he pretended to think for a moment “i can’t stay mad at you.” he said and you cringed at his cheesy words. “c’mere, cuddle me.” you said reaching your arm out to him.

and he did as you said and put his phone away and laid down beside you and you kissed his cheek. “also from now on, you can’t undress in front of me when i’m mad.” jimin said after laying down for a while.

“why?”

his cheeks got just a lil bit red before he opened his mouth, “it kinda turns me on..” he said. you just looked at him, “but i undress in front of you all the time..?” you questioned him.

“yeah but when i was jealous i thought that it was going to end in angry sex.” he said almost casually if it weren’t for the tint on his cheeks giving him away. “oh.” you said. “and then i looked at the nudes you sent me yesterday..” he said with a guilty look on his face. but you just chuckled. “you could have just put the thing you were mad at me for and ask me you know, i’m your girlfriend.” he nodded and the guilty face went away and was replaced with a smile and there was a comfortable silence. you tried to go to sleep but jimin had his eyes open and seemed like he was thinking hard. “are you not tired?” you said tiredly and he shook his head. jimin had messy hair and tired eyes, he looked so cute you just couldn’t help but give him a quick kiss but he pulled you closer.

“i know something we can do to tire me out.” he mumbled against your lips with a smile, “oh? you do..? what is it?” you played dumb, he just smiled wider and kissed you again.

answer: I go through it at least once a week but those recent pictures just fucked me up lol and it be like that sometimes 😂 also bon voyage didn’t help, every time he does something crazy or chaotic or funny I fall deeper in love 😭 it’s not just his perfect face and physique it’s his whole personality and he’s just so PRESENT and I wish he got more attention and credit and screentime because he’s fucking hilarious and entertaining idk why he’s been put in the back as if he’s just an empty pretty vase for such a long time. I’m glad Jin is steadily getting the appreciation he deserves tho, and the more I get to see of him the deeper I fall and I’m sure it’s like that for many fans 😊 MORE JIN CONTENT!!! I’m speaking this into existence for 2019!!!

Yoongi stares at Taehyung, eyes intent, lips parted. He asks, wry, “are you going to leave me again, Kim Taehyung?”

Taehyung’s eyes flicker like the heavy low of thunderstorms. Without hesitation, he answers with a sad, firm certainty.

body:
High school au!

(Basically I was bored one day and wrote this - a phone call between the reader and Yoongi, who is their bff. Enjoy!)

Yoongi still hasn’t showed up to class and the bell rang five minutes ago. Luckily, the teacher is late as well. You decide to call him. After the third ring, he picks up. His groggy voice makes you snicker, before you start scolding him.

“Hello-”

“MIN YOONGI YOU’RE THE CLASS PRESIDENT I DON’T CARE HOW MUCH YOU SLEPT. GET YOUR BUTT OVER HERE SO YOU CAN SAVE YOUR REPUTATION AND KEEP ME FROM MURDERING ANYONE.”

“I’d take you seriously if you weren’t whisper shouting like a goody two-shoes.”

“Says the guy in charge of class stuff, you teachers pet.”

“Euuugh im getting up just to show you my marks… I’m NOT a pet.”

“Yes yes, you’re a sleepy rock we know. Just come before I have to go give you homework tonight. I can’t go over or my parents will be pissed at both of us.”

“Like I’d do the homework.”

“Like you wouldn’t- STOP STALLING THE LATE BELL RANG.”
